reviewText: disappointment. dated. not good. do not buy. i recommend box of disorder or red bull rampage. they are more up to date with tricks, etc.

Thrill junkies will devour this collection of exclusive clips capturing West Coast mountain bikers in action on dirt ramps, street ramps, flat land and rocky terrain. Not-to-be-missed highlights include daredevil stunts from Shawn Butler and a trip to the picturesque Canadian Rockies, where professional riders take part in an unbelievable bicycle race.
